cc:Work.dc:title: Movie Title Rebus
cc:Work.dc:description: A rebus for the movie title "Titanic". TIE + (TANK - K) + (PICNIC - PICK). Typeface is Tuffy (public domain, created by Thatcher Ulrich) from openfontlibrary.org. Pictures from openclipart.org (wine bottle: sheikh_tuhin; wine glass: piotr_halas; cheese: nicubunu; sandwich: rg1024; apple: johnny_automatic; ant: Andy; tank: Anonymous; pick: Machovka) and http://jimmac.musichall.cz (tie: Jakub Steiner)
